#   /bin/ecology_manager/ — symbiosis shapes every food web
#   /usr/culture/ — cultural fusion, syncretism, conquest, assimilation
#   /net/technium/ — AI evolution as absorption of training data
#
# The fusion triad (fusion/possession/symbiosis) is as universal
# as the bond triad (ionic/covalent/metallic) in /lib/electron_bonding.so.
# Different vocabulary. Same geometry. Same universe.
